title: Custom Oak Cabinets, Walk-in Closets, Double Stainless Steel Sinks
posting_body: ['Located in the heart of Canyon Country near Santa Clarita, Diamond Park Apartments brings you incredible amenities and comfort in a beautiful and convenient Southern California location.', 'With several airy floor plans to choose from, top-of-the-line kitchen designs, private balconies and patios, and easy access to the best of Santa Clarita and Canyon Country, our one and two bedroom apartments for rent offer exquisite living at an affordable price.', 'At Diamond Park in Canyon Country, just minutes from the heart of Santa Clarita, CA we have apartments to meet all your needs for both space and style.', 'AMENITIES AND FEATURES', '-Lounging and Sunbathing Areas', '-Double Stainless Steel Sinks', '-On-site Maintenance', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-Soothing Whirlpool Spa/Hot Tub', '-Custom Oak Cabinets', '-Washer/Dryer in Each Apartment Home', '-Easy Access to Freeways & Shopping', '-Pre-Wired For Telephone and Cable', '-Carport Available', '-Unassigned Open Parking', '-Large Private Balcony/Patio', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'WEBSITE', '<URL>', 'ADDRESS', '27940 Solamint Rd., Canyon Country, CA 91387', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
